# JobTrackr frontend environment example
#
# The frontend has NO required secrets. It always calls the relative `/api`
# base path:
#   - in development, Vite proxies /api -> http://localhost:5080 (see vite.config.ts)
#   - in production, nginx forwards /api to the backend
#
# Copy this file to `.env` only if you need to override local behaviour.
# Nothing here is sensitive — never commit real secrets.

# Example (optional): if you later want the dev proxy target to be configurable,
# wire this into vite.config.ts. Not used by default.
# VITE_API_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:5080
